msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /mnt/c/Users/etrees/Desktop/private/spring-framework/framework-docs/modules/ROOT/pages/core/beans/context-introduction.adoc:928
msgid ""
"Here is an example of instrumentation in the "
"`AnnotationConfigApplicationContext`:"
