#. type: delimited block =
#: /mnt/c/Users/etrees/Desktop/private/spring-framework/framework-docs/modules/ROOT/pages/core/beans/context-introduction.adoc:993
msgid ""
"You can register an `ApplicationContext` by using the "
"`ContextLoaderListener`, as the following example shows:"
